2d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15138,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/19\/vanity-garments\/","url_meta":{"origin":25041,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Vanity: Humiliation for clothing in ostentation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 19, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever wears a garment in vanity, Allah will make him wear a garment of humiliation on the Day of Resurrection, then He will set it ablaze with fire.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Majah 3607 Grade: Hasan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15161,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/21\/prophet-sometimes-green\/","url_meta":{"origin":25041,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Clothes: Permission to wear green clothing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Rimthah reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, wearing two green cloaks. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2812 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0631\u0650\u0645\u0652\u062b\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0639